---
title: Deep Dish Mushroom and Mozza Pizza with Arugula-Spinach Balsamic Salad
description: Tonights Chicago-inspired deep dish pizza is filled to the brim with cremini mushrooms, savoury marinara sauce and fresh ooey-gooey mozzarella. Nows that's a pizza pie!
